  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK305">
<l>taṉṉaittāṉ kākkiṟ ciṉaṅkākka kāvākkāṟ</l>
<l>ṟaṉṉaiyē kolluñ ciṉam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a man would guard himself, let him guard against anger; if he do not guard it, anger will kill him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
